  "key": "ko.kinship-address-context",
  "value": {
    "instruction": "Treat bare Korean social address forms such as 누나, 오빠, 형, and 언니 as forms of address, not proof of a family relationship. Translate a family relationship only when surrounding speech supplies explicit kinship evidence, including terms such as 친누나 or 매형."
  },
